es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑<br />\n<br />\n當年叫APM 好似因為用開得晏做賣點"},{"pid":"195ce31825a6cd6f6c1fb9e6be039f24b57cd1f2","tid":1132714,"uid":233593,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"當年初開業個場規定啲舖閂12點，後來真係無人流先改到11點準閂門<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"adcd88f8b2d98f3062cb5d0c6f5f7fc27a3bdc0b","tid":1132714,"uid":34132,"like":231,"dislike":2,"score":229,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"apm的名稱是把am（上午）和pm（下午）融合起來，與商場提倡的夜間消閒概念互相呼應。因而大部份店舖的營業時間直至凌晨，甚至通宵營業。而夜間消閒的概念，是源於近年來在職人士的工作時間越來越長，壓力亦越來越大，然而香港的購物商場多數只營業至晚上十時，令這些人士在下班後幾乎無處消閒減壓。發展商有見及此，特別把apm定位為一個店舖營業時間特長的商場，讓顧客不再受時間束縛，盡情購物消閒。"},{"pid":"b791510344515ec70cc1367e7b4ca7ad089db070","tid":1132714,"uid":87820,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a3943ae0e474cf75b99baa302f5c29f27d00db53","tid":1132714,"uid":31173,"like":6,"dislike":307,"score":-301,"quote":{"pid":"e9593f478007a21b3cefce18fb779fbfad0d8825","tid":1132714,"uid":225871,"like":383,"dislike":1,"score":382,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:36:33.000Z","msg":"am同pm都開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"Wowowowow<br />\n<br />\nHahahahaha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aa897f1dc354a0ca040e16176f6a398571b9dc","tid":1132714,"uid":22716,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"quote":{"pid":"a3943ae0e474cf75b99baa302f5c29f27d00db53","tid":1132714,"uid":31173,"like":6,"dislike":307,"score":-301,"quote":{"pid":"